{"name": "odoo12-addon-fieldservice-account-analytic", "metadata": {"name": "odoo12-addon-fieldservice-account-analytic", "version": "12.0.3.3.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/field-service", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo12-addon-fieldservice-account", "odoo"], "summary": "Track analytic accounts on Field Service locations and orders", "upload_time": 1582090771}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Ffield--service-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/field-service\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/field-service/tree/12.0/fieldservice_account_analytic\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/field-service-12-0/field-service-12-0-fieldservice_account_analytic\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/264/12.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-bodedra: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/bodedra.png?size=40px\n    :alt: bodedra\n    :target: https://github.com/bodedra\n    ```\n  maintainer-brian10048: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/brian10048.png?size=40px\n    :alt: brian10048\n    :target: https://github.com/brian10048\n    ```\n  maintainer-osimallen: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/osimallen.png?size=40px\n    :alt: osimallen\n    :target: https://github.com/osimallen\n    ```\n---\n\n# Field Service - Analytic Accounting\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module adds the ability to track your analytic accounts on field\nservice orders.\nIt also adds the option to track the billing partner for field service\nlocations and orders.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nNo special installation instructions\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, you need to:\n\n- Go to Field Service > Master Data > Locations\n- Create or select a location and set their analytic account\n\n## Usage\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/field-service/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/field-service/issues/new?body=module:%20fieldservice_account_analytic%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Open Source Integrators\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Michael Allen \\<<mailto:mallen@opensourceintegrators.com>>\n- Serpent Consulting Services Pvt. Ltd. \\<<mailto:support@serpentcs.com>>\n- Brian McMaster \\<<mailto:brian@mcmpest.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Open Source Integrators \\<<https://opensourceintegrators.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-osimallen }} {{ maintainer-brian10048 }} {{ maintainer-bodedra }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/field-service](https://github.com/OCA/field-service/tree/12.0/fieldservice_account_analytic) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard.fsm_wizard", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2018 Open Source Integrators", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard.fsm_wizard.FSMWizard", "bases": ["models.TransientModel"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard.fsm_wizard.FSMWizard._prepare_fsm_location", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "partner", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard.fsm_wizard.FSMWizard._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard.fsm_wizard", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.fieldservice_account_analytic.wizard..fsm_wizard", "project": null}}]}